history.content:
Are you curious about what roles exist in the animation industry? If so, come to WIA's Animation Production Panel on Wednesday, October 23rd to hear from three industry professionals -- Bridgette Powell (Software/Production Engineer at ILM), Brittany Graham (Environment Artist at ILMxLAB), and Mariana Galindo (Technical Director at Pixar). We will be discussing their careers, projects, path to the animation industry, and more!
We'd love to see you there, 6:00-7:30pm in Barrows 126! Panelists' backgrounds range across CS, engineering, and art so all students are welcome!

More details available on the event page -- https://www.facebook.com/events/535681170520735/
history.subject: Curious about CS in the animation industry?
